items.title: Thailand same-sex marriage law takes effect: "Every love is the same"
items.description: Hundreds of LGBTQ couples in Thailand get married as the country's landmark marriage equality law comes into effect.

items.title: Brothers say Hawaii police framed them for tourist's 1991 murder
items.description: Albert "Ian" Schweitzer, who spent over two decades in prison for the killing of Dana Ireland, was released in 2023 based on new evidence.

items.title: Idaho murders suspect's lawyers want DNA evidence thrown out
items.description: Bryan Kohberger is charged with four counts of murder in the deaths of Ethan Chapin, Xana Kernodle, Madison Mogen and Kaylee Goncalves.

items.title: Oscar nominations to be announced Thursday for 2025 awards
items.description: Nominations for the 97th annual Academy Awards are being announced Thursday morning. Watch live as the full list of Oscar nominees is unveiled.

items.title: Sepulveda Fire ignites near 405 Freeway, with temporary evacuation warnings in Bel Air
items.description: It was first reported just after 11 p.m. near northbound lanes of the freeway in Sherman Oaks, according to the Los Angeles Fire Department.
